Definition: the subject matter of a conversation or discussion
Example: he didn't want to discuss that subject; it was a very sensitive topic; his letters were always on the theme of love
Synonyms: topic, adj, pert, topical, theme, thematic, message, the, matter, of, a, conversation, or, discussion, he, didn, t, want, to, discuss, that, it, was, very, sensitive, his, letters, were, always, on, love
Category: noun.communication
